# glview

[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.com/toaarnio/glview.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.com/github/toaarnio/glview)

Lightning-fast image viewer with smooth zooming &amp; panning + HDR exposure control.

**Installing:**
```
pip install glview
```

**Usage:**
```
glview --help
```

